com.ibm.team.repository.common

Interface Rights


  • public interface Rights
    Interface containing constants for various kinds of permissions.

    Permissions are intentionally in ascending order: PERMISSION_UPDATE > PERMISSION_READ, PERMISSION_CREATE > PERMISSION_UPDATE.

    Since:
    0.5

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int PERMISSION_CREATE
      Permission constant (value 2) allowing creation of new artifacts.
      static int PERMISSION_READ
      Permission constant (value 0) allowing read/checkout of artifacts.
      static int PERMISSION_UPDATE
      Permission constant (value 1) allowing lock and/or check-in new versions of artifacts.
